  "detailed_description": "<strong>A world blanketed by endless snow...</strong><br><br>A neverending war, a land terrorised by bandits, the world has known only darkness since the great God DEUS gave his own life to defeat THE BLACK KNIGHT.<br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871670/extras/45b2ed99f788a891bd48f616c43c0e95.poster.avif?t=1652604764\" width=640 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871670/extras/45b2ed99f788a891bd48f616c43c0e95.webm?t=1652604764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871670/extras/45b2ed99f788a891bd48f616c43c0e95.mp4?t=1652604764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A dark, story heavy adventure:</strong> 4 - 5 hours of gameplay. <br></li><li><strong>A Stylised 2D art style: </strong> Heavily inspired by paper craft <br></li><li> <strong>Multiple POVs:</strong> Experience the story from the perspective of 3 main characters plus many more side characters. <br></li><li><strong>Countless choices to make:</strong> And multiple endings based on the choices you make</li></ul><br><strong><u>Before You Play</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871670/extras/af3fed57d001d795cac5d9e3bea19f70.poster.avif?t=1652604764\" width=640 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871670/extras/af3fed57d001d795cac5d9e3bea19f70.webm?t=1652604764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871670/extras/af3fed57d001d795cac5d9e3bea19f70.mp4?t=1652604764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>While inspired by many classic JRPG's and created in RPG Maker the game is a combatless experience focusing instead on choices and dialogue.<br><br>Dark themes, strong language and violence are common. If this is not something you are comfortable with this game may not be for you.",
